<div class="accordion" id="cookieHelpAccordion">
    <div class="accordion-item border-0">
        <h2 class="accordion-header">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed bg-transparent p-0 text-muted small" type="button"
                    data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#cookieHelpBody">
                <i class="fas fa-question-circle me-1"></i> How to get your cookie
            </button>
        </h2>
        <div id="cookieHelpBody" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#cookieHelpAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body px-0 pb-0 small">
                <ol class="mb-0">
                    <li>Log into <a href="https://www.patreon.com" target="_blank">Patreon</a> in your browser</li>
                    <li>Press <kbd>F12</kbd> to open DevTools, go to the <strong>Network</strong> tab, filter by <strong>XHR</strong></li>
                    <li>Visit any creator page and look for a <code>posts</code> request</li>
                    <li>Click the request, go to <strong>Headers</strong> tab</li>
                    <li>Find <strong>Cookie</strong> under Request Headers, right-click and <strong>Copy Value</strong></li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
